f suspension device it\\\u0027s hanging from, or is it just a parachute in the act of deploying or something?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Goddess Bhavani","CreatedById":14001,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-21T00:36:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EKerbtimus Prime has risen!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-21T01:40:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cp\u003EKerbtimus Prime has risen!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003Enot yet. it looks lousy.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://kerbalspaceprogram.com/forum/index.php?topic=6239.0\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ETHIS one\u003C/a\u003E is 8)\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Goddess Bhavani","CreatedById":14001,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-21T02:52:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EAll it needs now are lasers, autocannons and LRMs.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThen, pew pew pew sounds.\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}